            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "This survey is only related to Accounts and Admin department.\nNo doubt about teachers, they are very good and take good care of students. Make sure they understand the concept and help them to gain confidence while learning. 5 Stars to Teaching Staff.\nMeanwhile, Admin and Accounts department are make the school's name bad. They are simply non cooperative. I have experienced their response and it was very bad. They don't care what our need is or what we are trying to say, they respond very badly. My personal suggestion to School Staff is to make some improvements in this section.",
